  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, W-EP-04 probe)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is set at 3. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed; the 'Equivalency of input parameters' factor is carried as not-assessed on the grounds that the simulation inputs are considered self-evidently matched to the bench test conditions and therefore the factor is judged inapplicable in practice — however the encoding retains factorStatus 'not-assessed' rather than 'not-applicable', creating an epistemic gap at an elevated risk level.",
