    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors are assessed. Assessed factors collectively support a Low assurance level conclusion consistent with the MRL 3 context. The equivalency of input parameters factor was judged by the team to be self-evidently satisfied and was not formally assessed; the package is accepted on the basis that direct use of measured values as boundary conditions renders a formal equivalency study unnecessary. This judgment has not been independently verified and the factor remains encoded as not-assessed.",
